+====== h_config_save_rules =====
+<HTML>
+<HEAD>
+<TITLE>OPTION: <!--#echo var="VAR_save-rules"--></TITLE>
+</HEAD>
+<BODY>
+<H1>OPTION: <!--#echo var="VAR_save-rules"--></H1>
+
+<P> This option is used to specify which folder should be used to save a
